data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value:
This test utility shows:
- Connectivity status. This uses events and timers to show how these methods can detect USB changes
- Read ADC values – the read button
- Read initialisation status of the LED and sets state of an LED attached to b.5 - the check box
- Use of LibKWINUSB library to call the GCB USB stack
- Polls the microcontroller every 10 secs after the last USB transmission
- Recovery from USB physical D- and D+ errors by using a state engine.
- Example code documentation for this application and the Great Cow BASIC solution.
Enjoy
